{"tid":766828,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李慧琼冀回鄉證加入支那身份證號碼方便港人","createTime":"2018-08-04T03:06:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-04T11:52:35.000Z","uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"63d01cc78f41b5472b3354d10983c92d66d43e54","tid":766828,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T03:06:10.000Z","msg":"國務院昨日公布取消現時港澳台在支那就業的行政許可申請。民建聯立法會議員李慧琼說，政策對青年人就業有實際作用，使他們有多一個選擇。<br />\n<br />\n她出席一個電台節目後說，希望在其他生活便利方面也能有類似的安排，例如與支那支付系統接軌。她亦希望，中共政府能考慮讓香港人申請支那身分證或在回鄉證加上支那身份證編號，減少港人在支那生活的障礙。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1410594-20180804.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1410594-20180804.htm&d=OyPra5W0UsMmW4Xh8JxRCAEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=a2362a43\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1410594-20180804.htm&h=f258b4f7\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1410594-20180804.htm</a>"},{"pid":"e64904d7ee26b25f0a138a5f715af2249e7eb4ee","tid":766828,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T03:06:36.000Z","msg":"公民黨立法會議員譚文豪認為，政策使港人回支那就業更方便，但他同時關注香港人口政策未有妥善處理，特區政府一方面不斷接受新移民，一方面叫港人去大灣區，認為做法有問題。"},{"pid":"819222b838ac1927ccb66de15c4ccceb6193164e","tid":766828,"uid":3244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T03:07:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ce491d496908a9390ad5158561ebb1e8bd67e965","tid":766828,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T04:05:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4407d08428304e552610564e64a09cd377117de","tid":766828,"uid":44673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"819222b838ac1927ccb66de15c4ccceb6193164e","tid":766828,"uid":3244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T03:07:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018